ext":"No more fear, no more shame to hold"},{"s":108.84,"e":111.5,"text":"Dust becomes diamonds when the spirit is bold"},{"s":111.5,"e":113.8,"text":"Fire under the banyan tree"},{"s":113.8,"e":116.06,"text":"Light in you and light in me"},{"s":116.42,"e":118.68,"text":"Karma move like a river deep"},{"s":118.68,"e":121.02,"text":"Dharma wake from the village sleep"},{"s":121.06,"e":123.68,"text":"Om, we rise with the morning sun"},{"s":123.68,"e":125.86,"text":"Many names, but the light is one"},{"s":125.86,"e":128.6,"text":"Shiva dance and the drums go wild"},{"s":128.6,"e":131.09,"text":"Krishna smiles in the forest child"},{"s":149.71,"e":153.29,"text":"In the jungle where the peacocks cry"},{"s":153.29,"e":155.57,"text":"Monsoon drums on the temple tile"},{"s":155.87,"e":158.29,"text":"Grandma tells what the sages saw"},{"s":158.29,"e":160.53,"text":"Life is love under cosmic law"},{"s":160.83,"e":163.37,"text":"Ram walked truth through the burning land"},{"s":163.37,"e":165.49,"text":"Sita held stars in her gentle hand"},{"s":165.89,"e":168.29,"text":"Arjuna shook with the war inside"},{"s":168.29,"e":170.79,"text":"Krishna said, “Stand in the Self, don’t hide”"},{"s":170.79,"e":173.29,"text":"Do your work, let the fruit go free"},{"s":173.29,"e":175.67,"text":"Serve the world, let the heart be clean"},{"s":175.67,"e":178.27,"text":"Ahimsa breath, compassion seed"},{"s":178.27,"e":180.69,"text":"Feed every soul, give every need"},{"s":180.69,"e":181.93,"text":"Who are we?"},{"s":181.97,"e":183.19,"text":"Light in clay"},{"s":183.19,"e":184.41,"text":"Where do we go?"},{"s":184.73,"e":185.69,"text":"Home one day"},{"s":185.69,"e":186.91,"text":"What do we seek?"},{"s":187.05,"e":188.25,"text":"Truth, not gold"},{"s":188.25,"e":189.47,"text":"What do we bring?"},{"s":189.47,"e":190.71,"text":"Love to hold"},{"s":190.71,"e":193.03,"text":"Dharma in the dirt, karma in the rain"},{"s":193.03,"e":195.65,"text":"Moksha in the fire burning through the chain"},{"s":195.65,"e":198.01,"text":"Devi in the mother, Shiva in the sky"},{"s":198.01,"e":200.71,"text":"Krishna in the laughter, Brahman never dies"},{"s":200.79,"e":203.07,"text":"Fire under the banyan tree"},{"s":203.07,"e":205.43,"text":"Light in you and light in me"},{"s":205.73,"e":208.19,"text":"Karma move like a river deep"},{"s":208.19,"e":210.49,"text":"Dharma wake from the village sleep"},{"s":210.49,"e":212.91,"text":"Om, we rise with the morning sun"},{"s":212.91,"e":215.35,"text":"Many names, but the light is one"},{"s":215.35,"e":218.05,"text":"Shiva dance and the drums go wild"},{"s":219.07,"e":224.07,"text":"Krishna smiles in the forest child"},{"s":230.41,"e":235.55,"text":"Under the banyan, under the moon"},{"s":235.49,"e":238.03,"text":"Drums in the jungle, hearts in tune"},{"s":238.03,"e":240.55,"text":"River is singing, smoke in the sky"},{"s":240.55,"e":247.49,"text":"Om in the breath, let the ego die"}],"duration":262.2,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.284Z","stats":{"whisperWords":473,"polishedWords":461,"matched":443,"matchRate":0.961}}